[Claude]: Now I have a good understanding of the package. JStachio is a compile-time Mustache templating engine for Java. Key observations:

1. It has an `Escaper` and `HtmlEscaper` system for output encoding
2. It has a `NoEscaper` / `PlainText` escaper that explicitly bypasses HTML encoding
3. It uses `TripleMustache` (unescaped output) in templates
4. Spring integration for web responses
5. Lambda support in templates

